                        ?><rs type="bibl" ref="">Lahdo 2010</rs><?oxy_comment_end?>) and, earlier, four articles (2001, 2002, 2004, 2015) on the village’s vernacular. Lahdo (2004) discusses the influence of Turkish on the town’s Arabic dialect. Lahdo (2015) contains two texts.</p>
